{
  "bio": [
    "Marc Fielmann is the CEO of Fielmann Group AG, Europe's leading optical company that operates stores and online shops across the continent and also in the United States.",
    "Guenther Fielmann handed over the company to his son Marc as the market leader in Germany, Austria, and Switzerland in 2018 with approximately 700 stores. As of now Fielmann operates around 1,300 stores.",
    "With revenues exceeding EUR 2 billion and some 24,000 employees, Fielmann serves more than 28 million customers.",
    "Fielmann holds a BSc from the London School of Economics and Poltical Science (LSE).",
    "He began working at the company in 2012 and took over the reigns from his father in 2019."
